author: crayyy_zee
description: Display Discord server limits including channels, roles, emojis, stickers, bitrate, file size, and video user limits with interactive progress bars and detailed breakdowns.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any end user data.
install_msg: Thanks for installing GuildLimits! Use `[p]guildlimits all` to view all server limits with interactive progress bars.
short: View Discord server limits and usage with interactive displays
